Helene Abrams at “consider yourself BRANDED” not only helped me pivot my business (organizedbyandrea.com) through Covid-19, she single-handedly took it to the next level. Helene is not only an amazing creative force, she is diverse in her skills and well equipped to address every marketing service you need. “It was so much easier than having to work with a copywriter and designer separately and managing deadlines.”

I can’t recommend her enough. She will elevate all of your ideas and make them better. You shouldn’t think twice just "considered yourself BRANDED" — you need it!

My two companies Newway,LLC and NewsomeColor were in desperate need of a facelift, rebrand and design connection to each other. Helene saw the big picture and made what seemed impossible “POSSIBLE!” Helene has incredible creative ability! She was a total and utter pleasure to work with. Her hard work, patience, and professionalism far exceeded my expectations. As a creative person myself, I was quite hands on! She never once made me feel like I was pestering her with questions. Any ideas I had she would expand on them to make them better, and her attitude was always positive and upbeat. I always felt like my project was priority number one. I love my new websites and soical media pages, as do my clients-you need to contact Helene and “consider yourself BRANDED!”

-Louise Newsome  | Newwwayllc |  Newsome Color

Helene Abrams is a true branding GENIUS!  From the very first telephone conversation, she walked me through her process and was very clear about the perfect concept for me, creating something completely new and innovative in my marketplace. Being part of this transformation and witnessing her work on my logo, tagline, website, jingle, social media branding was so AMAZING! When I look at the final product it is MINDBLOWING! She not only branded me but developed a unique creative marketing strategy that will effectively and efficiently help me with my goals. To anyone who is looking to brand their new business or give their business a face-lift, as a ongoing satisfied client, I highly recommend Helene at “consider yourself BRANDED”!
- Melissa Tswana | Affiliated Real Estate Agent with Citi Habitats
